Please give me the methodology introduction of the following given situation, and describe the importance of each of the tasks in about 500 words

As part of the overall Building services design solution you are required as part of the team to provide a scheme design solution to achieve a safe and sustainable design. 
You are required to perform the following tasks:-
a. Efficient Artificial lighting design solution;
b. Dynamic Fire and Egress simulation;
c. Energy modelling and simulation;
d. Sun shading Analysis;
e. Daylight Analysis;
